title: Wallpaper & nicnt files of Uploaded Kontakt library on here
description:
This is a list of almost all Kontakt libraries (mostly either uploaded by me or imafaggot) that missing wallpapers and NICNT files that allow you to add library to Kontakt.

Totally 22 8Dio fixes. 1 CineSamples. And 4 Spitfire Audio fixes.

INSTRUCTION:

- Unrar the files to the main folder of the named library.

- Open Kontakt and add the library.

Tested on Windows. Should work with Mac too.

If you have problem please post it here.
